  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was the one of the first few days that they did send telegrams also to Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know of anyone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I left the telegram in Yad Vashem.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the persons that got the telegram, and I told him, I don't see that it said it was 1940.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he says, don't worry, we know it was in 1940 because later on, they had already barracks and Jewish people were not notified when they-- and they had-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] what did they have?",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, then after this telegram, my mother was notify-- notified by Gestapo that she can come and they can talk to her about how did he died.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they said that he was-- this was a heart attack.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they told her if she will send-- I have in my mind 350 marks, then they would send us an urn with ashes.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But this was the most tragic time in my life and it's hard for me to talk about.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I think I told you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have it here.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
